main event: A UFO sighting of a round light green object with an orange trail was reported near Duncan, Oklahoma on 25 June 1955.
interesting points: The UFO appeared fuzzy and had a square cut-off trail at its trailing edge., The observation duration was approximately 5 seconds., A driver and his wife witnessed the object., The object reportedly made a 90-degree turn before disappearing., The report concluded that the object was likely a meteor.
sighted object: round light green object with an orange trail
